Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:03.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,正在交往的男友總這樣說我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:06.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根你真成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說實話我一直都覺得女生應該更麻煩一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可你既不黏著我 也從不說任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣的女生也是有的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:21.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我既想黏著他 也想說任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:25.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,僅僅是看見他和別的女生說話就有點嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵呜_GBK\b1\fs40\c&H005F535D\frz353.3\move(764,183,789,183,22,3066)}小\N武
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H005F535D\bord0\fn方正喵呜_GBK\b1\fs40\frz358.5\move(640,506,665,506,22,3066)}上\N根\N醬\N是\N壽\N司\N嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:28.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,從早安開始到晚安 想和他一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:32.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且這個距離 現在就想靠上去卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我要是提出這種要求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說不定會被認為是麻煩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:41.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛 剛田君你沒有想黏在一起的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在暫時沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,聽說那種關係一般無法長久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 這取決於程度不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 稍微的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如像牽著手一起散步之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,坐著的時候不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:08.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不願意的話也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可以喔 這點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:15.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不如說沒必要連這種小事也在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那再靠近一點也不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 上根你想這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那靠這麼近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:32.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然不要緊 我社團活動後的汗臭味…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個味道 好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 今天格外…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是不願意卿卿我我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 不會覺得很麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種程度還好 情侶的話不是很正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 那個 啊勒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:05.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不如說我才是擔心上根你不喜歡卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為一直感覺你很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可能沒考慮過這種事之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那剛田君你其實想卿卿我我的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 多少有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:23.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你早點說的話我也早就這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我還 可以說些任性的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 說什麼說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一直想試一次 原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,初吻的時候嗆著了! 初吻的時候嗆著了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才我 明明是第一次親吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼準備都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊… 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,初吻的時候咳嗽了… 初吻的時候咳嗽了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再試一次嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近一直在傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我班上的朋友和女朋友接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真厲害對吧 才交往不到三個月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,人不可貌相 真是神速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說來千秋 我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是的 我也覺得該談談這個事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,至今為止明明已經有過好幾次機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼球一直沒有進呢 教練?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:39.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還不是因為FW的千秋選手打從心底已經認輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真嚴格啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但 但是教練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,同伴的傳球故意果然也是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不全是千秋選手的責任…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那現在能來個傳球嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根選手和剛田選手 似乎是在公園裡進的球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,呃 呃呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:57.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大家可都覺得 我們兩個肯定早接吻了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 那個 交往到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和周圍人覺得我們有沒有接吻沒有關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最重要的 果然還是自己的節奏之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 真要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 因為 想做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,逼你做不情願的事我也很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才沒有不情願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底是加奈你一直在催我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,夠了 沒興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小加奈～ 生氣啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 小加奈?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗚啊 這怕是一時半晌不會理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,徹底的比賽終止…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 難道進入了加時賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒毛病!! 這絕對是一副在等我的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好啊 想上的話只有現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,射…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這角度稍微有點難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:57.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,幾乎很難靠近球門還感覺旁邊的視線有點厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這裡只好來點強硬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對偏啦啊啊啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是第一次親到女生的臉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好厲害!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,教練! 請讓我再來一次!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在我感覺能成 請再給次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好…好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還 還是算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.4,586.8)\fs40\c&H001E1E1E\b1\bord0}結\N束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 正解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,感覺我的英語變好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都是你的功勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那讓我揉一揉胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,赤木 這裡可是圖書室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:49.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本來是因為在家裡不能集中精神才到這來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:50.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼 你剛說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,請讓我揉一揉你的胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙明明腦瓜子還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但有時候真的是會說一些蠢話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:00.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蠢話?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種大庭廣眾之下 怎麼可能讓你碰胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:10.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果我強烈請求的話 你肯定會讓我揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸 你也這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說不定呢 你心腸比較軟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我才不是那種輕浮的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是難道只有我在忍耐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:27.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,亮子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我…並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不想更卿卿我我 一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:36.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧 讓你過來的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說了我並不想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒關係的啦 不用忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:53.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 反正沒人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是一下子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,作為交換讓我揉胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你要讓我一個人忍耐著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就算了 我反正也沒有那麼忍耐著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:06.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看 果然剛剛是在忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還不是你邀請的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那揉胸部也可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,隨你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我們繼續學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤? 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已經可以了 從一開始就沒打算揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然亮子你果然答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那為什麼要說想揉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:39.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我想讓你 知道我平時有多努力忍耐著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 搞得好像是我在撒嬌似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你能理解我就已經讓我很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 你在期待著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.4,586.8)\fs40\c&H001E1E1E\b1\bord0}結\N束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的戀愛不過是一束線香煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs37}註：線香菸花便是我們小時候玩的仙女棒煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,微小的戀愛燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,悄無聲息地燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:11.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但那鮮艷的光芒的殘像 在我的心裡仍…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這裡是我跟那個人第一次相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我真是個笨蛋啊 明明都已經被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香 香取前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊…勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:26.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是數子 細川數子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前跟前輩你在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:36.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我沒有能一一記住女生的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能稍微笑一下讓我看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到你的笑容的話可能會想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真棒!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那時候的小小貓咪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:47.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這些傷是怎麼弄的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,稍微打了一架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:49.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,救護車…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可以喔 小小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,會被那群人找到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在被追殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:10:00.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是我的錯 又讓別人的女人愛上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,太過分了 明明是對方的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 有過錯的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:08.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸 小小貓咪 怎麼樣我才能不受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好可憐 對前輩來說這是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再不走就要被他們發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這樣的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,家裡估計已經被監視了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,暫且先過一段隨性的流浪貓生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那來我家裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟我一起的話 會死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 完全不害怕的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你不懂啊 小小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真正的敵人不是追殺我的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:40.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是誰讓我變成這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能做到這種事情的人 就只有他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道是 GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,魔法～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只要戀愛的神明繼續我變得受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我肯定還會傷害到別人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我已經不想再傷害任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:03.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的!受著傷的是前輩你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢小貓咪 那是殘影喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真讓人吃驚呢 居然能跟上我的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算是我 只要認真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好了 到這為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對小貓咪來說這個動作還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:27.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,即便如此也要在前輩的身邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真是讓人頭痛的小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不 已經是出色的母豹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我就用一根手指阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請不要小看我 一根手指怎麼可能阻止現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:54.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你再這樣迷戀我的話 下次就不止是燒傷這麼簡單了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然我 果然我這種人對前輩而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}如果這樣也不在乎的話 燃燒下試試?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}開玩笑啦 讓學妹玩火的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我作為學長不是失格了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼會 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}為了不再這麼受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:15.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}乾脆我去把浪漫女神攻略掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在那之前 你可要小心戀愛之火喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:22.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}香取前輩!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 開端
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也會覺得很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}此時此刻也在想念著你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}喜歡與討厭相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的機率的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還是跨不出這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們的關係可以說是曖昧模糊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雖然無聊但還是希望能感受到屬於我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要珍視這份感情
